Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a sharp and precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once he gets started, you can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In today's episode, a car explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:08.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The adult world is a bit complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.56,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:12.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:15.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:39.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nishitama City
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at so intently?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just remembering the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The past?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may not know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but in the past, in every bank, there was a space open for the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had a bulletin board with messages like "Looking for nice home for kitten," or such.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I once put up a "please hire tutor" message on the board too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, were you tutoring, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have money, but I married your mother while I was still a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I had no choice but to do part-time work to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and Mom had quite a tough time, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the one who really had a tough time must've been the one who was taught by Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about? I was a pretty good tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As proof of that, the student I taught for 3 years entered the law department of Jonan University!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used to live in Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:04:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't been in this part of Beika Town often, but it hasn't changed much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you haven't seen her in a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her name is Megumi Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and her father is a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used to let me drink beer after lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, {\i1}that's{\i0} why he lasted for 3 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. What's with that car anyway, speeding like that on such a narrow road?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her house is right around that tobacco shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} person got married long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and doesn't live there anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's also a possibility that she's still single!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not thinking of anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come off it. What can I do with you kids along with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've really grown to be an adult, haven't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, {\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi is inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:45.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A fire extinguisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Beika Central Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're in shock because it is right after the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but may I ask you a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your name is Megumi Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:41.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Megumi Sakihara (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who died in the car that exploded
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is your younger sister, Hiromi Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.72,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiromi Tanaka (32)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An explosive was rigged onto the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explosives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the explosive was hooked up under the car along with an ignition device.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably rigged so that when the tires turned, an explosion would occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also remember that the car exploded soon after she started to back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I know how you feel, but let me ask a few more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That house you came out of is your parents' house, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My parents died in a car accident 6 months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister's been living there alone ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that car your sister's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the car that I drove all the way here from my residence in Nishitama today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister's car was at an auto shop for inspection,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I parked my car in the empty garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'm not good at backing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister offered to back it out for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then {\i1}you{\i0} were the one who was actually supposed to be driving that car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the killer mistakenly killed your younger sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what on earth is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what time did you leave your residence in Nishitama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little before 2:00 in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything unusual about the car back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time did you arrive at your parents' house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was around 2:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The explosion occurred at 3:00 sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, then most likely the explosive was rigged to the car during those 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea as to who it may be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know if anyone may have a grudge on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was being watched by a man at a supermarket near my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pretended not to notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I felt quite uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that man's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a very distinctive face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get an officer who is good at drawing portraits,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we'd like your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't even occur to me that I'd be meeting you again like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew that you had become a famous detective, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brag to my friends that you used to be my tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to track down the killer who did such a terrible thing to Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do that, {\i1}Sensei{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a surprise that she used to be a student of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also knew her younger sister too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was still in middle school back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and used to always serve us cake and tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike her older sister Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, who was quiet and easy-going,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} used to joke a lot, had many friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was outgoing and very cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to have changed much to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} graduated from college, she went to work for a securities company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She stayed there only for a short while and got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has no children, but seems to be living a peaceful life as a housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, on the contrary, after graduating from a two-year college,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{worked as a free part-timer,}drifted from job to job,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even after she turned 30, still seemed to be living a carefree life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the investigation on Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s going to take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The portrait is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he look like that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember the driver who blitzed past us on our way to Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he was wearing sunglasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his hairstyle and chin look exactly the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks just like that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what time did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 10 minutes before we got to Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at the alley about 500 meters before reaching her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, he could've been fleeing after setting up the explosive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the model and license number of the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a red RV, with a Shinjuku license number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search for it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife? How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but are you Kazuo Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:29.14,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kazuo Sakihara (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a call from the police, saying that my wife had a bombing accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry. Your wife is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your wife's younger sister passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hiromi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An explosive was rigged to your wife's car,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was driving the car in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, have you ever seen anyone like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sure is acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Investigation at the scene of the explosion has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the portrait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and the others seem to have seen him near the scene of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's reliable evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw him among the papers of the case that Detective Sato is handling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the woman who was killed in Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only took a glimpse, but he looks a lot like the victim's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, check on that portrait right away and contact Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Metropolitan Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They certainly look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've met the man himself, so I think there is no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the husband of the woman who was stabbed to death on her way home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from shopping at a convenience store at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:34.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiromasa Takahashi (33)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Hiromasa Takahashi, age 33,\Nan employee at a chemicals company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And over here is his wife, the victim,\NSachiko Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're investigating it as a random murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she was covered by a very expensive insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her husband, who is in debt, was also a suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he has a perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Takahashi's car a red RV with a Shinjuku license plate number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, it is quite definite that the man we saw was Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if he works for a chemicals company, he could easily get a hold of explosives too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A random murder case and a bombing incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they seem to be two very different cases, but maybe there's a link?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although there are no names that correlate in both cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too many things fit in for this to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Another deduction could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a cool looking badge there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please exchange it with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, this is not a badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please exchange it, please exchange it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand that you can't exchange it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exchange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an exchange murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exchange murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, both incidents connect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An agreement of an exchange murder was made between Kazuo Sakihara and Hiromasa Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, Sakihara kills Takahashi's wife, Sachiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, Takahashi tried to kill Sakihara's wife, Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Sakihara saw the sketch of Takahashi at the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he looked right shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because he knew that Takahashi was the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} want to kill Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can be imagined from his remark when he found out that the one who died
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was his wife's younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.29,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}H-Hiromi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His remark sounded obviously more intimate than just a brother-in-law relationship with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate the case with all what was pointed out just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in a rush, but are you going anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest on charges of assault and battery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's explosives in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Sakihara saw the sketch,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he informed Takahashi to run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that, in turn, was a breakthrough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that Takahashi had admitted the crime, Sakihara turned himself in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and confessed that he has killed Takahashi's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to have talked Takahashi into committing an exchange murder
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when they happened to see each other at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They never met after that first meeting, and all arrangements were done by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They used a pay phone, so that no evidence would be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara had a phone exclusively for himself in his study upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to have made sure to take all calls with this phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be why Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't realize what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what was Sakihara's motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you had deduced,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara had an intimate relationship with Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s younger sister, Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara seems to have thought up killing Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to come up with cash
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for opening a boutique that Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she wanted to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because if Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dies, all the money that he inherits from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the money for the insurance that she is covered by,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would become his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel! Poor Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, although it seems she couldn't make herself believe it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All she could do after finding it to be true was cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's understandable, because although she wasn't involved in the crime at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she was backstabbed by her own younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check up on her in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the case has been solved and is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help her out as an old friend, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later, then, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Inspector Megure.{needs fixgo-kurou-sama deshita}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wonder if everything has really been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I feel something is being overlooked...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:21.53,Character Card,,0,0,0,,A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You promised to meet Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at 1:00, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! We're an hour early!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go have some coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:34.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:39.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't this the supermarket where Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} mentioned she saw Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, isn't that Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She backed out of a parking space that narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But didn't Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since I'm not good at backing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:36.14,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}my sister was getting out the car for me, so I could head on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She offered to back it out for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:44.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what I saw doesn't look like a person who has trouble backing up her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:49.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then why did Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} ask Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} to take her place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:55.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Because of that, the explosion killed Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can this really be an unlucky coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} already knew the whole plot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This case isn't solved yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has something to do with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} you know is the Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in her high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could've changed after becoming an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has not changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's what she used to be before!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to believe so, don't you, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But actually she's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:15.22,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Window
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:21.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, the solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:24.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Whether love or deductions, I'll do it!
